data.description: Move-in ready, beautiful, brick ranch in a desirable neighborhood is ready for it’s new owners. Located within Waynesville school district and is only minutes away from Caesar Creek State Park, the Renaissance Festival, and plenty of shopping in the village of Waynesville. This home welcomes you with a spacious living room, featuring vaulted ceilings and overlooking your private back yard. 3 bedrooms, including an owner’s suite with a walk-in closet, 2 full bathrooms, and a 2 car garage. Fresh paint and new carpet throughout. Schedule your showing today!
